videos.description: Nolan Cressler hits 3 from the wing to give Vanderbilt a 7-0 lead
videos.headline: Cressler's 3 gives Vandy early lead

videos.description: Matthew Fisher-Davis gets the block and Payton Willis drains the 3-pointer on the other side.
videos.headline: Defense leads to offense with Vanderbilt 3-pointer

videos.description: Bam Adebayo throws it down
videos.headline: Big Bad Bam

videos.description: Mychal Mulder gets the big time dunk for Kentucky.
videos.headline: Mulder throws one down on Senior Night

videos.description: Bam Adebayo finishes and gets the and-1 as Kentucky cuts Vandy's lead to 4
videos.headline: Perfect give and go helps Kentucky cut into lead

videos.description: John Calipari talks about his team missing every open shot in the first half.
videos.headline: Kentucky's coach John Calipari talks about his team's first half play

videos.description: After Kentucky steal, Malik Monk drives to hoop for 2 and-1
videos.headline: Kentucky defense leads to layup

videos.description: Nolan Cressler finds Joe Toye at the corner who drains the 3-pointer for Vanderbilt.
videos.headline: Vandy uses the San Antonio Spurs ball rotation for corner 3-pointer

videos.description: Matthew Fisher-Davis beats the pressure defense and feeds Luke Kornet for the dunk
videos.headline: Vandy breaks the press with Kornet dunk

videos.description: Jeff Roberson sees the shot clock expiring,  and hacks up a 3-pointer that goes for Vanderbilt.
videos.headline: Vandy's Roberson drains 3-pointer as shot clock expires

videos.description: Derek Willis gets the block getting Kentucky out and running where Isaiah Briscoe finds Monk for the layup plus the foul.
videos.headline: Monk gets the lucky bounce for and-1 layup

videos.description: 7 footer Luke Kornet finds himself wide open and nails the 3
videos.headline: Kornet drains the deep 3

videos.description: De'Aaron Fox drives strong to the hoop for the layup as Kentucky cuts Vandy lead to 54-52
videos.headline: Kentucky pulls within 2

videos.description: De'Aaron Fox finds Derek Willis who drains the 3-pointer for Kentucky.
videos.headline: Willis gives Kentucky its first lead of the game with 3-pointer

videos.description: After trailing most of the night, Kentucky's Malik Monk hits the 3 to give the Wildcats a late 7 point lead over Vanderbilt.
videos.headline: Monk caps off Kentucky's comeback with 3-pointer

videos.description: Luke Kornet drains 3-pointer to cut into Kentucky's lead.
videos.headline: Vandy still not out yet with 3-pointer

videos.description: Kentucky coach John Calipari discusses his team's 73-67 comeback victory over Vanderbilt.
videos.headline: Calipari: 'We stayed together'

videos.description: Derek Willis explains his proposal and comeback victory over Vanderbilt.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Willis talks about his proposal

videos.description: Sean Farnham and Joe Tessitore break down Kentucky's wild comeback win over Vanderbilt and look at where the Wildcats sit in the SEC standings.
videos.headline: Kentucky sits atop the SEC standings

videos.description: Malik Monk scores 20 points in the second half to lead No. 9 Kentucky past a 19-point deficit to a 73-67 victory over Vanderbilt.
videos.headline: Monk rallies Kentucky past Vandy
